claim: Within 14 plays , the Dolphins had reached the 65 yards line on the Dolphins .
truth: The Dolphins drove 65 yards in 14 plays to the Patriots 25 , but on 4th-and-18 , Daniel Thomas could only gain 10 yards and the Dolphins turned the ball over on downs .

claim: The severe acute respiratory syndrome had less than 8,300 cases and less than 800 deaths between November 2002 and July 2003 .
truth: Between November 2002 and July 2003 , an outbreak of SARS in southern China caused an eventual 8,098 cases , resulting in 774 deaths reported in 37 countries , with the majority of cases in China ( 9.6 % fatality rate ) according to the World Health Organization ( WHO ) .

claim: The urban subdivision of Reading had an estimated population of more than 250,000 according to the 2011 census .
truth: In the 2011 census , the urban area around Reading had an estimated population of 318,014 , making it one of the largest towns in the UK without city status .

claim: During one game of their 2016 season , the American football team The New England Patriots drove 72 yards after forcing the Browns to punt .
truth: After forcing the Browns to punt , the Patriots drove 72 yards , all the way to the Browns 1-yard line , but Blount could n't get in on 3rd or 4th down , and the Patriots turned the ball over on downs .

claim: Over 650,000 COVID-19 infections and more than 29,950 deaths have been recorded in more than 150 countries .
truth: more than 645,000 cases of COVID-19 have been reported in over 190 countries and territories , resulting in approximately 29,900 deaths .

claim: After July 31 , 2019 , See You Again reported 4.1 billion views on YouTube .
truth: As of August 1 , 2019 , the video has received over 4.1 billion views on YouTube making it the third most viewed video on the website .

claim: Malaysia had more than 4,000 confirmed coronavirus cases including more than 65 deaths by April 9 , 2020 .
truth: Within a few weeks , Malaysia recorded the largest cumulative number of confirmed COVID-19 infections in Southeast Asia ; as of 9 April 2020 , there are 4,228 confirmed cases in the country , with 67 deaths reported .

claim: There were less than 390,000 COVID-19 cases worldwide by March 24 , 2020 .
truth: As of 24 March , more than 386,000 cases of COVID-19 have been reported in more than 190 countries and territories , resulting in more than 16,700 deaths and more than 102,000 recoveries .

claim: Brazil had reported less than 50,000 coronavirus cases by April 23 , 2020 , including less than 3,500 deaths .
truth: As of 23 April 2020 , 49,492 cases have been confirmed in the country , causing 3,313 deaths .

claim: There were more than 225,500 COVID-19 cases in more than 150 countries by March 19 , 2020 .
truth: As of 19 March , more than 226,000 cases of COVID-19 have been reported in over 150 countries and territories , resulting in more than 9,200 deaths and 85,000 recoveries .

claim: Amongst the 73 people evacuated by Ukraine from Wuhan , less than 6 of them were from the Dominican Republic .
truth: The original number of Nepalese to be evacuated was 185 , however , only 175 were evacuated , as 4 of them decided to stay back and 6 were barred to board the flight due to medical reasons . *On 19 February , Ukraine evacuated 73 people from Wuhan , which included 48 Ukrainian citizens and 29 foreign nationals ( 8 nationals from Argentina , 5 from Dominican Republic , 5 from Ecuador , 4 from Salvador , 2 from Kazakhstan , 2 from Costa Rica , and one each from Israel , Montenegro and Panama ) .

claim: Beginning February 6 , 2020 , fewer than 28,282 coronavirus cases were reported in China .
truth: As of 6 February 2020 , 28,281 cases have been confirmed , including in every province-level division of China .

claim: Jong-hoon left F.T . Island in 2019 due to his involvement in the Burning Sun scandal .
truth: On March 14 , 2019 , Jong-hoon left the band and retired from the entertainment industry after being involved in the Burning Sun scandal , where he was part of a group chat in which some members shared videos of sexual activities recorded without the consent of the other party. ? oid=213 & aid=0001093008 Hong-gi began his mandatory military service on September 30 , 2019 , becoming the first F.T . Island member to enlist .

claim: Italy has received the aid of three medical teams and a donation of 40 tons of medical supplies from China .
truth: However , some reports claimed that China had sold back to Italy the same PPE Italy had donated to China , but thus far China has already sent 3 medical teams and donated over 40 tons of medical supplies to Italy .

claim: From the 2016 Census , Odia , the language of Odisha is spoken by over 40 million people .
truth: Odia ( formerly known as Oriya ) is the official and most widely spoken language , spoken by 60 million according to the 2016 Census .
